version_description: The chords that I put is more accurate than original version.
This song is played easiest in standard with Capo on the 1st fret (F). Transpose the chords a 1/2 step down to get the actual chords of the song.
This version has the right chords and includes the outro.
Chords for parallel harmonica playing in D. I sang this song with my girlfriend using these chords.
Easier for Novices to play and it allows for more embelishments - hammer ons pull offs of chords better for solo players with the capo here.
